Paper: hep-th/9710011

Date: 1997-10-02

Title: Skyrmions and domain walls

Authors: B. Piette and W.J. Zakrzewski

Comments: latex, 5 pages. Proceedings of the Soliton conference (Kingston 1997)

We study the 3+1 dimensional Skyrme model with a mass term different from theusual one. We show that this new model possesses domain walls solutions. Wedescribe how, in the equivalent 2+1 dimensional model, the Skyrmion is absorbedby the wall.